vercel/ai#9595.body:
### Description

Anthropic just announced Agent Skills and it would be great to have support for it within the AI SDK.

**Here are key resources for it**

- Blog post: [https://anthropic.com/engineering/equipping-agents-for-the-real-world-with-agent-skills](https://t.co/yAkxZCRwJD)
- Docs: [https://docs.claude.com/en/docs/agents-and-tools/agent-skills/overview](https://t.co/7cELqPpdg5)
- Cookbook: [https://github.com/anthropics/claude-cookbooks/tree/main/skills](https://t.co/W2mBWBGic6)
- Using Agent Skills with the API https://docs.claude.com/en/api/skills-guide
- Public repo with skills: https://github.com/anthropics/skills
- https://simonwillison.net/2025/Oct/16/claude-skills/

**Architecture**

<img width="1200" height="676" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ac6024cd-8b92-485b-9083-c45dd3b3fcec" />

**Example code from Anthropic's SDK to use Skills via the API**

```ts
import Anthropic from '@anthropic-ai/sdk';

const client = new Anthropic();

const response = await client.messages.create({
  model: 'claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929',
  max_tokens: 4096,
  betas: ['code-execution-2025-08-25', 'skills-2025-10-02'],
  container: {
    skills: [
      {
        type: 'anthropic',
        skill_id: 'pptx',
        version: 'latest'
      }
    ]
  },
  messages: [{
    role: 'user',
    content: 'Create a presentation about renewable energy'
  }],
  tools: [{
    type: 'code_execution_20250825',
    name: 'code_execution'
  }]
});
```

Currently, AI SDK already supports [Claude's Code Execution tool](https://github.com/vercel/ai/issues/9433), which is needed to use Skills. We would also need to find a way to pass down container.skills and the right Beta headers to the Anthropic provider.

On the same note, it would be interesting to find a way to abstract Agent Skills to run with any LLM provider and also with code execution on device. 

### AI SDK Version

- [ai@5.0.75](https://github.com/vercel/ai/releases/tag/ai%405.0.75)

### Code of Conduct

- [x] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct

**Update**

I've created a PR to implement this: [feat: implement support for Claude Agent Skills #9597](https://github.com/vercel/ai/pull/9597)

