this is probably a bug from Anthropic, and i'm not sure if there is much the AI SDK can do. but its worth reporting here because a) this is very bad in production, it basically renders the tool search tool useless, and b) maybe the AI SDK team is in a better position to raise Anthropic's attention to this serious issue.

